          <blockquote>
              <p>For what it’s worth, here’s what I settled on for <em><a href="https://spoutinglore.blogspot.com/2018/07/stonetop.html" rel="nofollow noopener">Stonetop</a></em>:</p>
<p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="//gauntlet-discourse-store.s3.dualstack.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/original/2X/c/c2fbd948fa8e5d29d69a5a5bcf6b7927e6d8675d.png" data-download-href="/uploads/short-url/rOUdbSyeomcXruwIZkC2TrRGyD3.png?dl=1" title="image" rel="nofollow noopener"><img src="//gauntlet-discourse-store.s3.dualstack.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/optimized/2X/c/c2fbd948fa8e5d29d69a5a5bcf6b7927e6d8675d_2_665x500.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="rOUdbSyeomcXruwIZkC2TrRGyD3" width="665" height="500" srcset="//gauntlet-discourse-store.s3.dualstack.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/optimized/2X/c/c2fbd948fa8e5d29d69a5a5bcf6b7927e6d8675d_2_665x500.png, //gauntlet-discourse-store.s3.dualstack.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/optimized/2X/c/c2fbd948fa8e5d29d69a5a5bcf6b7927e6d8675d_2_997x750.png 1.5x, //gauntlet-discourse-store.s3.dualstack.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/original/2X/c/c2fbd948fa8e5d29d69a5a5bcf6b7927e6d8675d.png 2x" data-small-upload="//gauntlet-discourse-store.s3.dualstack.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/optimized/2X/c/c2fbd948fa8e5d29d69a5a5bcf6b7927e6d8675d_2_10x10.png"><div class="meta">
<svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#far-image"></use></svg><span class="filename">image</span><span class="informations">1305×980 428 KB</span><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#discourse-expand"></use></svg>
</div></a></div></p>
<p>The “Getting Started” chapter then includes instructions to start “session 0” with players spending 10-15 minutes to review this document (and the more detailed setting notes that follow) and then discuss:</p>
<ul>
<li>Setting (open Q&amp;A, talk about what excites/interests you)</li>
<li>Expectations (specifically premise, agenda, and principles)</li>
<li>Tone &amp; content (including a procedure for establishing excluded, veiled, and specially handled content, and a place to record that on the “group” character sheet for the village)</li>
<li>From there, make characters and introduce them</li>
</ul>
<p>Initial feedback from new playtest groups has been very positive.</p>
          </blockquote>
          <p><a href="https://forums.gauntlet-rpg.com/t/games-with-a-good-cats-one-pager/5837/5">Read full topic</a></p>
